org.fxmisc.wellbehaved.event.experimental

Interface InputMap<E extends Event>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - type of events that this InputMap may handle. That is, InputMap<E> certainly does not handle any events that are not of type E; it does not mean it handles any event of type E.
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface InputMap<E extends Event>
